{"tid":941141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個乞人憎同事好鍾意r新同事做fd","createTime":"2018-12-14T13:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T23:56:18.000Z","uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c94ebc9197661f14e2c5e72cc1243493542133a0","tid":941141,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:54:42.000Z","msg":"呢個乞人憎同事 平時態度好串嘴<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 佢問人今日晏晝係食乜 個同事好心答<br />\n<br />\n佢今日食牛腩飯 之後條友就話算啦 食咩<br />\n<br />\n都無所謂啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我係旁聽者 都喺心入面 <span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n屌</span>咗聲出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以佢成日都俾好多同事講是非<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 當佢一見到啲fg嘅同事/intern <br />\n<br />\n就賴係同人fd咁撩人傾計 有啲真係中佢計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但公道啲講 我諗佢唔知自己語氣有問題 <br />\n<br />\n你哋有冇啲同事都係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20000772e51ef41c58f3e1bdd7594ae9939208a0","tid":941141,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"puah"},{"pid":"2713f04ac3a45581c7183e4308cdb9d1fd826746","tid":941141,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:01:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8667b9621de2ed637db8113739a30a7e65060218","tid":941141,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f110793dfa6ca6eb760da11b06dabab62e81b4bc","tid":941141,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:04:00.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起個同事<br />\n當初我地係新人啦 佢走黎搭嗲<br />\n之後聽返 原來佢得罪曬啲人先要係咁r新同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61137872107c610e5f255d1029a5f2a1a49dfae0","tid":941141,"uid":164932,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"係我有問題定你有問題 點解我睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" 